{"tid":430163,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《A.I.C.O. -Incarnation-》將於2018年春季播映","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T14:30:54.000Z","uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c9303892d5b42ba7db7a79931fa92990642e6d","tid":430163,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5bmpOOfjLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ5bmpOOfjLM&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=49a24a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5bmpOOfjLM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/222441_d1563d41edeb0ab01de4fa24d61d95a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F222441_d1563d41edeb0ab01de4fa24d61d95a5.jpg&h=fb3c6d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「你&hellip;&hellip;已經不再是人類了。」世界知名影片《交響詩篇艾蕾卡 7》及《我的英雄學院》的動畫製作公司 Bones 與《翠星上的加爾岡緹亞》和《鋼之鍊金術師：嘆息之丘的聖星》的導演村田和也，攜手呈獻原創生化科幻動作影集。<br />\n<br />\n2035 年的日本，某個研究計畫發生了一場名為「大爆炸」的意外，失去控制的人工生命體「大麻煩」因而產生，佔據了整個黑部峽谷。曾被譽為人類希望的研究重鎮就此遭政府全面封鎖。兩年後，在「大爆炸」中失去家人的 15 歲少女橘愛子，從轉學生神崎雄哉得知令人難以置信的事實。她的體內隱藏著一個秘密，而一切謎題的解答就在「大爆炸」的中心地「原初點」。少年與少女相遇，人類的命運掌握在兩人手中，他們將揭曉什麼樣的嶄新真相？ Netflix 獨家，2018 年春季上線<br />\n<br />\n呢套睇落好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcabeb9c5e2071259f1de4a482050d5ee7d625a","tid":430163,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"聽落唔知點解感覺同亡念之扎姆德好似有d似<br />\n而且又係Bones嘅"},{"pid":"d206603837ff99e80148440e0685157504eec0db","tid":430163,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5bmpOOfjLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ5bmpOOfjLM&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7